'''Twilight lizards''' were small [[Reptile/Legends|reptiles]] native to [[Yavin 13/Legends|Yavin 13]]. With sizes ranging from 0.6 to 1.0 [[Meter/Legends|meters]] long, the lizards had four clawed legs, and a long tail. They emerged only during twilight hours, seeking out small [[Insect/Legends|bugs]] to eat, and retained virtually their entire weight in liquid; on the [[Desert/Legends|desert]] [[Planet/Legends|world]], this made them valuable prey for larger creatures. The nomadic [[Slith]] valued the lizards as trading commodities.<ref name="GG2">''[[Galaxy Guide 2: Yavin and Bespin]]''</ref>

